 The two bots smiled as Galvatron easily finished the bot off.  They followed 
the bots back to the base. Guiledart touched a few keys and shut the door 
behind them to cut off any escape for the new prisoner. "Yes with your 
permission Magmatron I can make this bot one of our own without any chance of 
defiance."

--part1_9b.1086e5c0.27b2024f_boundary
